law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 406, sec. 336, effective January 1, 1975. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1358-1, 1358-2, 1358-3.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Fraudulent severance of timber, buildings, minerals and fixtures from land under mortgage or vendor's lien.
